snippet.title: Need for Speed Carbon - Mobile trailer
snippet.description:
Finally, the DOOM RPG trailer has been surpassed.  This is the best mobile phone game's trailer ever!

Suprisingly, this one didn't take me long to do but I am very proud to have created it. A very cool trailer that many people thought was better than the console effort.  I'm very glad.

If you would like to see more cool trailer from me then just type "TrojanX" in the search box.
